item.title: Why I am special
item.author: jsacosta1103@gmail.com (Jerad Acosta)
item.description: Part of: Why I am special May 24 or 26 dates and times matched with earth quake in peru I think (fake internet?) So much carry on. But needed to get the words down for a second time. The first time I wrote this by hand it seemed to convince my most powerful opponents to wait rather than cut me from the story. * This happened right after the grocery store when I felt a huge shift.
